pipx install spotdl
```

#### Fedora
```bash
sudo dnf install yt-dlp ffmpeg python3-textual pipx
pipx install spotdl
```

#### Windows
```powershell
winget install yt-dlp.yt-dlp Gyan.FFmpeg Microsoft.WindowsTerminal
pip install textual spotdl
```

